> HWD_VIIF_L2_VDM_ALIGN) != 0U)) {
> > +                  return -EINVAL;
> > +    }
> > +
> > +    if ((size != 0U && size < HWD_VIIF_L2_UNDIST_MIN_TABLE_SIZE) ||
> > +        size > HWD_VIIF_L2_UNDIST_MAX_TABLE_SIZE) {
> > +                  return -EINVAL;
> > +    }
> > +
> > +    if ((size % 4U) != 0U)
> 
> size % 4 is enough.

I'll drop comparison with zero.

